(a^b)^c=\underbrace{(a^b)\times(a^b)\times\cdots\times(a^b)}_{c\text{ times}}=
\underbrace{\left(\underbrace{a\times a\times\cdots \times a}_{b\text{ times}}\right)\times\left(\underbrace{a\times a\times\cdots \times a}_{b\text{ times}}\right)\times\cdots\times \left(\underbrace{a\times a\times\cdots \times a}_{b\text{ times}}\right)}_{c\text{ times}}=
\underbrace{a\times a\times \cdots\times a}_{bc\text{ times}}=a^{bc}
